Charlie Park is Downtown Tallahassee’s Premier Event Space
Host your special occasion with us! We pride ourselves on being Downtown Tallahassee's Premier Event Space and can't wait to celebrate with you.
Book Your Event
A Space for Every Occasion
Our breathtaking view of Cascades Park is the perfect backdrop for any event— large or small. From intimate 12 person birthday celebrations to 100 person four-course plated dinners, Charlie Park’s unique layout can accommodate your special occasion. We will even open for Lunch during the week and/or dinner Sunday night, when we are typically closed, to host your event.
If you are interested in hosting with us or learning more please fill out the form below and a member of our events team will help to make your vision become a reality.
